{
  "storyId": "lorecraft_tutorial_v2",
  "title": "Lorecraft Tutorial: The World That Notices",
  "startSectionId": "S1",
  "save": {
    "defaults": {
      "sectionId": "S1",
      "stats": { "W": 2, "E": 2, "A": 2, "L": 2, "T": 2, "H": 2 },
      "resources": { "HP": 10, "REPUTATION": 0 },
      "progress": { "level": 1, "xp": 0 },
      "flags": {
        "first_death_warned": false,
        "candle_lit": false
      },
      "inventory": {
        "consumables": ["healing_salve"],
        "weapons": ["rusty_dagger"],
        "armors": ["leather_jerkin"],
        "specialItems": ["candle"]
      },
      "equipped": { "weapon": "rusty_dagger", "armor": "leather_jerkin", "special": "candle" }
    }
  },
  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "S1",
      "text": [
        "You arrive in Lorecraft with the feeling that the world has already been paying attention.",
        "Not judging—just… noticing.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "VerseCraft basics: You make choices. Choices can change state. State changes what choices appear." },
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "WEALTH is your profile: W E A L T H. HP is your survival meter." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "S1_CHAR", "text": "Open Character (see WEALTH + loadout).", "to": "CHARACTER" },
        { "id": "S1_INV", "text": "Open Inventory (tabs + item buttons).", "to": "INVENTORY" },
        { "id": "S1_GO", "text": "Begin the tutorial run.", "to": "S2" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S2",
      "text": [
        "A corridor stretches ahead. Signs are mounted politely at eye level—like the building is trying to be helpful.",
        "A small plaque reads: NOTICE WHAT CHANGES.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "Tutorial promise: If HP changes, you will see why." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "S2_LEFT", "text": "Go left (darker hallway).", "to": "S3" },
        { "id": "S2_RIGHT", "text": "Go right (door labeled ARCHIVE).", "to": "S4" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S3",
      "text": [
        "The left hall is dim and stubborn about it. The ceiling lights hum but refuse to fully commit.",
        "Ahead, something on the floor catches the light—too late to be friendly.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "StoryLogic moment: your Candle only works when the scene supports it." },
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "Open Inventory → Special → Use Candle." }
      ],
      "itemUse": {
        "candle": {
          "ops": [
            { "op": "SET_FLAG", "key": "candle_lit", "value": true },
            {
              "op": "APPEND_TEXT",
              "lines": [
                { "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "The candle flares to life. The hallway gives up a few secrets." }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "consume": false
        },
        "healing_salve": {
          "ops": [
            { "op": "ADD_RESOURCE", "resource": "HP", "amount": 2 },
            { "op": "APPEND_TEXT", "lines": [{ "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "You apply the salve. HP +2." }] }
          ],
          "consume": true
        }
      },
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "S3_SAFE",
          "text": "Proceed carefully with candlelight.",
          "requires": { "flagTrue": "candle_lit" },
          "to": "S5"
        },
        {
          "id": "S3_RISK",
          "text": "Proceed without a light (risk it).",
          "to": "S5",
          "onChoose": [
            {
              "op": "APPEND_TEXT",
              "lines": [
                { "__sys": true, "tier": "explicit", "text": "You misstep in the dark and get clipped by something sharp." }
              ]
            },
            { "op": "ADD_RESOURCE", "resource": "HP", "amount": -2 },
            { "op": "APPEND_TEXT", "lines": [{ "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "HP -2." }] }
          ]
        },
        { "id": "S3_BACK", "text": "Back to the main corridor.", "to": "S2" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S4",
      "text": [
        "ARCHIVE smells like paper that survived something dramatic.",
        "A rulecard sits on the nearest shelf, face-up like it wants to be found."
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "S4_RULES", "text": "Read the rulecard.", "to": "S6" },
        { "id": "S4_LEAVE", "text": "Leave the ARCHIVE.", "to": "S2" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S5",
      "text": [
        "Past the hazard, the hallway opens into a small chamber with a metal bowl set on a pedestal.",
        "It looks ceremonial. Which is never reassuring.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "Next is a small danger event to demonstrate fair HP penalties + feedback." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "S5_TOUCH", "text": "Touch the bowl.", "to": "S7" },
        { "id": "S5_LEAVE", "text": "Back away.", "to": "S2" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S6",
      "text": [
        "The rulecard reads:",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "WEALTH helps you choose. HP helps you survive." },
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "Tutorial rule: WEALTH won’t increase here. Progress comes later via XP + leveling." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "S6_RETURN", "text": "Return to the corridor.", "to": "S2" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S7",
      "text": [
        "The instant your fingers touch the bowl, the air tightens.",
        "A sting snaps across your skin—fast, rude, instructional."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "S7_PULL",
          "text": "Pull back immediately.",
          "to": "S8",
          "onChoose": [
            { "op": "APPEND_TEXT", "lines": [{ "__sys": true, "tier": "explicit", "text": "You got nicked. It hurts, but it’s manageable." }] },
            { "op": "ADD_RESOURCE", "resource": "HP", "amount": -1 },
            { "op": "APPEND_TEXT", "lines": [{ "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "HP -1." }] }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "S7_COMMIT",
          "text": "Commit (take what’s inside).",
          "to": "S9",
          "onChoose": [
            { "op": "APPEND_TEXT", "lines": [{ "__sys": true, "tier": "explicit", "text": "You force it. The bowl bites back." }] },
            { "op": "ADD_RESOURCE", "resource": "HP", "amount": -2 },
            { "op": "APPEND_TEXT", "lines": [{ "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "HP -2." }] }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S8",
      "text": [
        "You shake out your hand and glare at the bowl like it’s a person who owes you money.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "If you want: try using Healing Salve (Consumables tab) when the story allows it." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "S8_TRY", "text": "Try again, carefully.", "to": "S7" },
        { "id": "S8_EXIT", "text": "Leave the chamber.", "to": "S10" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S9",
      "text": [
        "You grit your teeth, endure, and take the lesson the hard way.",
        "Your hand comes away with something small—warm at the edges—like it wants to be important later.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "This is VerseCraft’s core: the world reacts to choices and loadout, immediately." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "S9_EXIT", "text": "Leave the chamber.", "to": "S10" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S10",
      "text": [
        "You return to the corridor. The building seems… satisfied.",
        "A sign appears where there wasn’t one before:",
        "TRY SAVE/LOAD NOW.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "HUD → Save. Refresh the page. Continue → Load. (Local saves on this device.)" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "S10_MENU", "text": "Return to Main Menu.", "to": "MENU" },
        { "id": "S10_REPLAY", "text": "Restart Lorecraft tutorial.", "to": "S1" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}